### Autenticação
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@pleno.com",
  "password": "senha123"
}

### Refresh
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "<token>"
}

### Criar município
POST http://localhost:3000/api/municipalities
Authorization: Bearer <token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Cidade Exemplo",
  "state": "SP"
}

### Criar mensagem agendada
POST http://localhost:3000/api/messages
Authorization: Bearer <token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Motivação do dia 1",
  "content": "Vamos juntos na jornada!",
  "type": "DAILY",
  "sendDate": "2024-12-01T12:00:00Z",
  "targetAudience": "ALL"
}

### Upload de imagem
POST http://localhost:3000/api/uploads
Authorization: Bearer <token>
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

file=@/path/to/photo.jpg
